===Etymology===
From earlier 水 (みづ, midzu/midu), attested in 1711 in the Konkoukenshuu (混効験集). The word underwent a pronunciation change due to the shifting of /u/ to /i/ after alveolar consonants. Cognate with {{cog|ja|水|tr=mizu}}, {{cog|ojp|-}} {{m|ja|水|tr=midu}}.

